text:
<@U3SCKQB4P> - hard to say what the issue is here w/o a little more detail on your setup.  error code 14 might indicate you are trying to communicate with a service on there wrong endpoint.  Can you provide:

1) hfc version
2) fabric version
3) env - Host operating system, Docker, native, Docker on Vagrant, etc

After I connected to the eventhub as per instructions on <https://hyperledger-fabric.readthedocs.io/en/v0.6/v0.6_migration/>, the deploy complete event is not ‘heard’ anymore by hfc, causing the message 'timed out waiting for transaction to complete’.
